#* c. '''1606''', {{w|William Shakespeare}}, ''{{w|Antony and Cleopatra}}'', Act II, Scene 2,<sup>[http://www.opensourceshakespeare.org/views/plays/play_view.php?WorkID=antonycleo&Scope=entire&pleasewait=1&msg=pl]</sup>
